<h4 style="text-align: center"> A guest has posted a non-refundable reservation on www.vacancytravel.com.
 </h4>

<%= render 'layouts/spacer', height: '25px' %>

<table class='row'>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <h5>Reservation Details</h5>
      <%= render 'mailers/listing_confirmed', listing: @listing, buyer_switch: false  %>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<%= render 'layouts/spacer', height: '25px'  %>

<table class='row'>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <h5>Seller Information</h5>
      <%= render 'mailers/seller_info', seller: @listing.user %>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<%= render 'layouts/spacer', height: '25px' %>

<table class='row'>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <h5>Next Steps</h5>
      <ul>
        <li><p><strong>Login</strong> - Login in to the Admin Dashboard at <a href="https://www.vacancytravel.com/hginapa">VacancyTravel.com</a> with the Admin login you were provided during training.  If you need help finding that info please email us at sales@vacancytravel.com</p></li>
        <li><p><strong>Confirm</strong> - Find the listing matching details from this email. Click the CONFIRMED link (listing valid – per hotel records) if all the reservation details are correct.</p></li>
        <li><p><strong>Listings</strong> - All listings that need to be confirmed will be listed on the Confirmation Pending tab.</p></li>
        <li><p><strong>Fraud</strong> - If any of the info is incorrect or you believe there may be fraudulent activity, please click the “<strong>Delete Listing</strong>” red button at the bottom of the reservation.  The listing will be deleted from our system and the guest will be notified that their reservation will not be posted.</p></li>
        <li><p><strong>Help</strong> - If the guest calls with any questions or concerns, please have them contact us at either help@vacancytravel.com or by phone at (415)500-5018</p></li>
      </ul>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

